quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  114,1,"Sọ pé: \"Mo sá di Olúwa àwọn ènìyàn"
  114,2,Ọba àwọn ènìyàn
  114,3,Ọlọ́hun àwọn ènìyàn
  114,4,"níbi aburú (Èṣù) oníròyíròyí, olùsásẹ́yìn (fún ẹni t’ó bá dárúkọ Allāh)"
  114,5,(Èṣù ni) ẹni tí ó ń kó ròyíròyí sínú àwọn ọkàn ènìyàn
  114,6,(Èṣù náà) wà nínú àlùjànnú àti ènìyàn